<html>
    <head>
        <title>Your OTP Code</title>
        <style>
            body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; } .container {
            margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; max-width: 600px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius:
            4px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h1 { color: #0056b3; } .otp { font-size:
            1.2em; color: #0056b3; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class='container'>
            <h1>Hello, {{name}}!</h1>
            <p>We received a request to use your email for logging into our system. Please use the
                OTP code below to proceed:</p>
            <p class='otp'>Your OTP Code: <strong>{{otp}}</strong></p>
            <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Thank you,</p>
            <p>The Support Team</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>